name: TICKETMASTERAI
description: This is TICKETMASTERAI. He has been tasked with escorting holders out of the trenches. We are going to make it out of the trenches with this one! This is your ticket out. Ticket ensures admittance.

pitches.pitch: This is a pitch to just spread awareness about the project and get people to support the character as well as the Operation videos the team and I work on. These videos are shorts that will showcase the character as well as progressive narrative for the character and the project as we navigate this crypto market.
